            <div>
              <h4>Case Study System (6 Published)</h4>
              <p>Custom case study architecture with 6 fully written case studies. Each follows a clear problem-approach-results structure. Indexed by service type and industry so prospects can find the most relevant work quickly.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">👤</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Team Profile Pages (8 Consultants)</h4>
              <p>Individual profile pages for all 8 consultants with specific expertise areas, certifications, professional background, and a direct contact link. Structured to pass the credibility check that enterprise procurement teams run on vendor staff.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">🔍</span>
            <div>
              <h4>8 Service Pages Optimised for US Keywords</h4>
              <p>Dedicated pages for cloud infrastructure, cybersecurity consulting, digital transformation, managed services, IT strategy, data governance, DevOps consulting, and Microsoft 365 migration. Each page targets specific US enterprise search queries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">⚙️</span>
            <div>
              <h4>HubSpot Form Integration</h4>
              <p>All contact and enquiry forms connected directly to HubSpot CRM. Leads are assigned, tracked, and acknowledged automatically. No more submissions lost in a shared inbox.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="cs-deliverable">
            <span class="cs-deliverable-icon" aria-hidden="true">📝</span>
            <div>
              <h4>Blog Setup with 4 Initial Articles</h4>
              <p>Blog infrastructure configured with category taxonomy, author bylines, and reading time estimates. Four initial articles published on cloud migration, cybersecurity strategy, digital transformation, and IT vendor selection, each optimised for long-tail enterprise search queries.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>


<!-- ============================================================
